<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/cefc1e178a82b9018b3ecedb798da9773812ef43.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>英国报姐</strong>
<span>知名中英文化自由撰稿人</span>
